  "body": "### Description\n\nConfiguration options like `quarkus.config-tracking.hash-options` (from #34713) should be respected in the Gradle plugin when:\r\n* adding the hashed config options to the task-inputs (to avoid leaking sensitive information there)\r\n* dumping the configuration (via `QuarkusShowEffectiveConfig` and `QuarkusBuildTask.generateBuild()`)\r\n\r\nAlso write the config-options from the Gradle plugin to the same location, using the same conventions.\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
